ABAKALIKI – The National Youth Service Corps (NYSC) has applauded Governor David Umahi of Ebonyi State for renovating its orientation camp in Afikpo. The state director of the scheme, Mrs. Ann Ibe, said the Afikpo camp is now one of the best in the country. Ibe spoke in Abakaliki on Wednesday while chatting with newsmen. She commended Governor Umahi for what she described as his fatherly disposition and huge interest towards the success of the scheme in the state. Mrs. Ibe called on all corps members in the state to complement the governor’s gesture by adapting adequately to the expectations of the scheme and to discharge their primary a